Title: Abrahamson_2000_IMRCoefficients
Description: This class encapsulates all the coefficients needed to calculate the Mean and StdDev for the Abrahamson_2000_IMR. One instance of this class holds the set of coefficients for each period (one row of their tables 3/4 (horz) or 5/6 (vert)).
